# 📚 RAG System V2 — Documentación Técnica Completa

> **Objetivo**: Sistema de Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) de máxima precisión para consultar documentos internos. Usado por operadores que atienden al público y necesitan respuestas exactas extraídas de los documentos cargados.

---

## 1. Arquitectura General

```mermaid
graph LR
    subgraph Frontend ["Frontend (Vite + React)"]
        UI[UI Chat Interface]
        DocPanel[Document Panel]
        APIClient[API Client]
    end

    subgraph Backend ["Backend (Python FastAPI)"]
        Main[main.py<br>FastAPI App]
        ChatRoute[routes/chat.py]
        DocRoute[routes/documents.py]
        RAG[services/rag.py<br>Pipeline V2]
        DocProc[services/document_processor.py]
        Chunker[services/chunker.py]
        Embeds[services/embeddings.py]
        Config[config.py]
    end

    subgraph External ["Servicios Externos"]
        OpenAI[OpenAI API<br>GPT-4o + Embeddings]
        Supabase[Supabase<br>PostgreSQL + pgvector]
    end

    UI --> APIClient
    DocPanel --> APIClient
    APIClient -->|HTTP Proxy :5173→:8000| Main
    Main --> ChatRoute
    Main --> DocRoute
    ChatRoute --> RAG
    DocRoute --> DocProc
    DocRoute --> Chunker
    DocRoute --> Embeds
    RAG --> Embeds
    RAG --> OpenAI
    Embeds --> OpenAI
    Embeds --> Supabase
    DocProc -.->|Texto limpio| Chunker
    Chunker -.->|Chunks| Embeds
```

