## 9. API Endpoints

### 9.1 Documentos

| Método | Ruta | Descripción |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/upload` | Subir documento (FormData con campo `file`) |
| `GET` | `/api/documents` | Listar documentos únicos (agrupados por filename) |
| `DELETE` | `/api/documents?filename=X` | Eliminar documento y todos sus chunks |

**POST /api/upload — Response:**
```json
{
  "message": "Documento 'poliza.pdf' procesado exitosamente",
  "filename": "poliza.pdf",
  "file_type": ".pdf",
  "total_chunks": 45,
  "stored_chunks": 45,
  "content_preview": "Primeros 300 caracteres...",
  "reindexed": false
}
```

**GET /api/documents — Response:**
```json
{
  "documents": [
    {
      "filename": "poliza.pdf",
      "file_type": ".pdf",
      "file_size": 128000,
      "total_chunks": 45,
      "created_at": "2026-03-09T22:00:00Z"
    }
  ],
  "total_documents": 1
}
```

### 9.2 Chat

| Método | Ruta | Descripción |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/api/chat` | Enviar pregunta RAG |
| `GET` | `/api/conversations` | Listar conversaciones (últimas 50) |
| `GET` | `/api/conversations/{id}/messages` | Obtener mensajes de una conversación |
| `DELETE` | `/api/conversations/{id}` | Eliminar conversación y mensajes |

**POST /api/chat — Request:**
```json
{
  "question": "¿Cuál es la cobertura del celular?",
  "conversation_id": null
}
```

**POST /api/chat — Response:**
```json
{
  "answer": "Según el documento...",
  "sources": [
    {
      "filename": "poliza.pdf",
      "file_type": ".pdf",
      "similarity": 0.782,
      "rerank_score": 9,
      "chunks_used": 3
    }
  ],
  "documents_found": 6,
  "model": "gpt-4o",
  "conversation_id": "uuid-...",
  "pipeline": {
    "hyde_generated": true,
    "multi_queries": 3,
    "total_searched": 75,
    "unique_results": 32,
    "reranked_kept": 6
  }
}
```

